%% Volume = Activity × Average ticket.
%% Micro tools: high frequency, low average ticket. Privacy improves sustained usage and reduces long-term profiling risk.
%% High-value services: lower frequency, high ticket and high sensitivity. Privacy improves willingness-to-transact and liquidity.
